annotations.description: The Iron Ranger is a tiki inspired bourbon cocktail from San Diego barman Eric Castro. Castro who earned his chops working at Bourbon & Branch in San Francis...
annotations.title: Modern Classic: Iron Ranger

textContent:
2oz (60ml) Bourbon
1oz (30ml) Pineapple Juice
.75oz (22.5ml) Lemon Juice
.5oz (15ml) Simple Syrup
.5oz (15ml) Velvet Falernum
2 Dashes Angostura Bitters
Garnish Mint Sprig and Cinnamon Stick

Whip shake and pour. 
Top with crushed ice.
